c: 6
v: 6
t: "Ese ntibabona ko twarimbuye abantu benshi mbere yabo twari twarahaye ubushobozi ku isi tutigeze duha mwe (abahakanyi)? Twabamanuriye imvura nyinshi (barakungahara), ndetse tubashyiriraho imigezi itemba aho batuye. Nuko turabarimbura kubera ibyaha byabo, maze turema abandi bantu nyuma yabo"